    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Strategy for the Prevention of Torture sets out FCO policy and offers guidance to FCO posts on how they can further the torture prevention agenda overseas. This will primarily involve working in partnership with other countries and organisations to tackle the problem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
